 breakaway (Item# BA-P) for $.45 (C):\r\n- Option A: located at the back of the neck.\r\n- Option B: located on the side of the strap.</p><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">BA-P Back</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Option A: located at the back of the neck</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">BA-P Side</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Option B: located on the side of the strap</p></div></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Personalization</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Create added value by including individual names or consecutive numbers. Adds 3-5 working days.</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">Lanyard Personalization</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>Repeat Order w/ New Imprint 2nd Side</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">Repeat Orders: FREE set-up for same imprint on both sides; $20.00 (G) for different imprint on second side.</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">HWS3/4-repeat</p></div>\n</details>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500 mt-4\">Final quote may reflect selected options, proofs, rush, or freight beyond list pricing.</p>\n</div>","salesToolsHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p><strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">Pitch this SKU</strong> — 3/4&quot; Heavy Weight Satin Lanyard. Lead with use case (uniforms, retail, teams, recognition), then minimums and timeline. Reference included services from “Price includes” in the Description tab when present (e.g. setup, virtual proof, shipping offers).</p>\n<ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-2\">\n<li>Quote style <span class=\"font-mono text-neutral-900\">HWS3/4</span> on proposals and POs.</li>\n<li>Offer virtual proofs and artwork checks before production.</li>\n<li>Cross-sell with hats, bags, or jackets for kit programs.</li>\n<li>For decoration and imprint methods, follow supplier notes in the Description tab.</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Approved partners can request internal sell sheets, comparison matrices, and margin guidance from the A Design Line team.</p>\n</div>","inventoryHtml":"<div class=\"space-y-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-800\">\n<p>Merchandise is <strong class=\"text-neutral-900\">typically sourced to order</strong>. Stock and availability may vary by supplier and season.</p>\n<p>Supplier-stated production window: <strong>3 days</strong> (not including transit).</p>\n<p>Contact the studio for <strong>rush</strong> feasibility, <strong>split shipments</strong>, or <strong>multi-location</strong> drops before placing large orders.</p>\n<p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-500\">Minimum order quantity: <strong class=\"text-neutral-800\">50</strong> units (per catalog line).</p>\n</div>"}